data.description: Stunning 2 story on cul-de-sac with no back or right side neighbors nestled in highly desired Harmony. Gorgeous elevation with oversized front porch. 5 bedrooms (2 down) & 4 full baths (2 down)! 5th BR/study down has full closet & adjoining bath. Vinyl plank flooring in main areas, TONS OF STORAGE, 2nd bedroom down could be the perfect office if you only need 4 bedrooms as it is very private. floor to ceiling stone fireplace, full gutters with leaf guard, island kitchen with granite counters, bar seating, painted cabinets, stainless steel appliances & walk-in pantry. Primary bedroom with bay window sitting area. Primary ensuite features an oversized shower & double sinks. Upstairs offers a game room, 3 generously sized bedrooms & 2 full baths. The extended covered back patio offers roller sun shades, 2 fans & a gas stub. Huge back yard w/room for a pool, play set & garden. Shed stays. Exterior perimeter has recessed security lighting & extra long driveway. Floor plan & Top 10 attached.
